.container
    .jumbotron.subhead
        %h1 Modules
        %p.lead Game Settings
    %section
        .row
            = partial('modules_sidebar')
            .col-sm-9
                .page-header
                    %h1 TNT
                :markdown
                    You can modify TNT explosion & placing behavior with this module. Destruction of terrain can be easily disabled with the blockdamage element. If it is set to `false` the yield element will have no effect since there won't be any block drops. TNT damage can be further limited with the [disable damage module](/modules/disabledamage#block_explosion).

                    By default dispensers containing TNT will ignite their TNT when exploded. This behavior can be customized with the `<dispenser-tnt-limit>` and `<dispenser-tnt-multiplier>` elements, setting either of these to 0 will disable it.  


                    <br/>
                %h5 TNT Module Elements
                .table-responsive
                    %table.table.table-striped.table-hover.table-condensed.table-bordered
                        %thead
                            %tr
                                %th Element & Default Value
                                %th Description
                                %th Value
                        %tbody
                            %tr
                                %td
                                    %pre
                                        %code= html_escape('<instantignite> false')
                                %td Instantly ignite TNT when placed.
                                %td
                                    %span.label.label-primary true/false
                            %tr
                                %td
                                    %pre
                                        %code= html_escape('<blockdamage> true')
                                %td Specify if TNT destroys the terrain.
                                %td
                                    %span.label.label-primary true/false
                            %tr
                                %td
                                    %pre
                                        %code= html_escape('<yield>')
                                %td
                                    Modify the amount of items dropped by the explosion as a percentage.<br/>
                                    %i Not valid when <code>blockdamage</code> is false.
                                %td
                                    %span.label.label-primary 0 - 1.0
                            %tr
                                %td
                                    %pre
                                        %code= html_escape('<power>')
                                %td
                                    Modify the explosions block radius.<br/>
                                %td
                                    %span.label.label-primary 0 - 20.0
                            %tr
                                %td
                                    %pre
                                        %code= html_escape('<fuse>')
                                %td
                                    Time till the TNT explodes once it is ignited.<br/>
                                    %i Must be a value less than 4 seconds since the TNT entity vanishes after that.
                                %td
                                    %a{:href => "/reference/time_periods"} Time Period
                            %tr
                                %td
                                    %pre
                                        %code= html_escape('<dispenser-tnt-limit> 16')
                                %td
                                    Max amount of TNT a dispenser ignites when exploded.
                                %td
                                    %span.label.label-primary 0 - 64
                            %tr
                                %td
                                    %pre
                                        %code= html_escape('<dispenser-tnt-multiplier> 0.25')
                                %td
                                    Multiplier for the amount of TNT ignited when a dispenser is exploded.
                                %td
                                    %span.label.label-primary 0 - 2.0
                :markdown
                    Examples

                        <tnt>
                            <instantignite>on</instantignite>
                            <fuse>2s</fuse>
                        </tnt>

                        <tnt>
                            <dispenser-tnt-limit>8</dispenser-tnt-limit>
                            <dispenser-tnt-multiplier>1</dispenser-tnt-multiplier>
                        </tnt>
